p: Compounds 1, 3– 14 were identified based on comparison of their physical and spectral data with authentic samples or those already reported (Fig. 1). Their assignments were consistent with structures of: allantoin ( 1) [ 32], pyrimidine 2,4-(1 H,3 H)-dione ( 3) [ 33], cordialin A ( 4) and cordialin B ( 5) [ 34], quercetin ( 6) [ 35], myricetin ( 7) [ 36], genistein 4′- O-glucuronide ( 8) [ 37], methyl palmitate ( 9) [ 38], palmitic acid ( 10) [ 39], methyl (9 E,12 E)-octadeca-9,12-dienoate ( 11) [ 40], methyl oleate ( 12) [ 41], methyl tridecanoate ( 13) [ 42] and ( Z)-octadec-11-enoic acid ( 14) [ 43].
